HEADWORD: Natalitious
<hw>Na`ta*li"tious</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr> }</mhw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>natalitius</ets>, from
<ets>natalis</ets>. See <er>Natal</er>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to
one's birth or birthday, or one's nativity.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Natalitial</xex> poplar.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Evelyn.</au>
